@d5 6
a10 15
{\em Editors Note:} The Detect Aura is currently played with a much
weakened (that is not nearly as strict) version of intrinsic, for
example Callas (an Earth Mage) often asks ``Last magic to impact?''
and expects to get all magic, regardless of whether it was resisted or
not.  This should be possible since a rule change made all spells
impact upon their target, regardless of whether the target resisted or
not.  The last magic to impact is clearly separate from the last magic
to effect and both should be detectable.

