a108 8
those are properties of living beings only.  A question like "Last
spell to impact on this person" is likely to provide little
information if the last spell is no longer in effect on the person,
and certainly none if the spell was resisted -- it never became
intrinsic as it never affected the person (excepting those execrable
spells that have "half damage if resist").  If the GM is uncertain of
what the character is asking, they should request clarification prior
to answering.
